title: Being used as a political pawn: Sydney Sweeney accuses Trump supporters, rejects “MAGA Barbie” label
summary_full: Hollywood star Sydney Sweeney is navigating intense online speculation, particularly the "MAGA Barbie" label, which she insists others have attached to her. She emphasises her commitment to art and storytelling, not politics, expressing frustration at her identity being politicised. Sweeney desires to be known for her craft, not political discourse.
